Package: manaGENEment
Title: Tool for basic gene information management among different gene types
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexander",
           family = "Dell'Orti",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alexander.dellorti@mail.polimi.it")
Description: The manaGENEment package provides a set of S4 classes for handling different gene
 	types, in this version Protein Coding Genes, Long Non-Coding RNA (lncRNA) Genes and 
	microRNA Genes (miRNA). It offers functions to:
	- Create and manipulate gene objects.
	- Access and modify gene attributes (e.g., NCBI gene ID, HUGO symbol, RNA sequence).
	- Retrieve basic gene information (e.g., protein length, RNA length).
